; Coverage test for post.cc lookup shortcuts:
; Single-char variables a (amount), b (cost), n (count)
; Plus 'index' alias, 'calculated', 'cost_calculated'

2024/01/15 Test
    Expenses:Food    $50.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg --format '%(a)|%(b)|%(n)|%(index)|%(calculated)|%(cost_calculated)\n'
$50.00|$50.00|1|1|false|false
$-50.00|$-50.00|2|2|true|false
end test
